{"cid":"1596132533189636","cha_name":"赵露思","desc":"赵露思，1998年11月9日出生于四川成都，中国内地女演员。\n2016年，参加由芒果TV推出的歌手选秀节目《超级女声》海选活动。2017年，因参演古装言情剧《凤囚凰》从而进入演艺圈；同年7月，参演电影处女作《西游之净坛使者》。2018年，主演民国奇幻剧《青囊传》；4月25日，主演的古装言情奇幻网络剧《哦！我的皇帝陛下》在腾讯视频播出，在剧中饰演天生带有水逆体质的少女洛菲菲。2019年1月12日，在第三届金骨朵网络影视盛典中获得年度网络潜力演员奖。7月5日，主演的古装甜宠剧《天雷一部之春花秋月》在优酷播出，在剧中饰演上官春花。同日，发行单曲《恋爱脑少女》。11月8日，参加的综艺节目《演技派》播出。","schema":"aweme://aweme/challenge/detail?cid=1596132533189636","author":{"uid":"66754937719","short_id":"63791100","nickname":"彤","gender":2,"signature":"","avatar_larger":{"uri":"1080x1080/172880000c3c25c724265","url_list":["https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/172880000c3c25c724265.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p6.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/172880000c3c25c724265.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p26.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/172880000c3c25c724265.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_thumb":{"uri":"100x100/172880000c3c25c724265","url_list":["https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/172880000c3c25c724265.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p26.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/172880000c3c25c724265.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/172880000c3c25c724265.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_medium":{"uri":"720x720/172880000c3c25c724265","url_list":["https://p6.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/172880000c3c25c724265.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/172880000c3c25c724265.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/172880000c3c25c724265.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"birthday":"","is_verified":true,"follow_status":0,"aweme_count":0,"following_count":0,"follower_count":0,"favoriting_count":0,"total_favorited":0,"is_block":false,"hide_search":false,"constellation":6,"location":"","hide_location":false,"weibo_verify":"","custom_verify":"","unique_id":"","bind_phone":"","special_lock":1,"need_recommend":0,"is_binded_weibo":false,"weibo_name":"","weibo_schema":"","weibo_url":"","story_open":false,"story_count":0, ⚠️只要走路，全程直播！

user.signature:
一对80后搞笑小夫妻，初中相识，看对方不顺眼多年。终于在2014年看对眼了！
小时候学费靠跟着爸爸一起抓黄鳝，泥鳅维持。
坚持真实户外土货打野
喜欢挖泥鳅，除鼠，捉鱼虾，摸螺，钓鳝鱼的关注我带大家回忆童年趣事。
